org.zaproxy.zap.utils

Class PagingTableModel<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.table.AbstractTableModel
      • org.zaproxy.zap.utils.PagingTableModel<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, TableModel

    public abstract class PagingTableModel<T>
extends AbstractTableModel
    Asked Brian Cole (bassclar@world.oberlin.edu, http://bitguru.com) if I can base my code for ZAP on his PagingTableModel that I found here: http://www.coderanch.com/t/345383/GUI/java/JTable-Paging

    This model has got only MAX_PAGE_SIZE rows paged in at a time, but shows the scrollbar for all entries.

    Removed simulation code, added type parameter and abstract methods.
